Package: withcon
Type: Package
Title: Close Connections Automatically
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: c(
  person("Kota", "Mori", email = "kmori05@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides functionality similar to the `with` clause in Python.
    It automatically closes connections after a series of operations and 
    also when an exception occurs during the operations.
